Package eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.pivoting.metrics

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChebyshevDistance<V>
    Implements calculation of Chebyshev distance between two multi-dimensional points.
    EuclideanDistance<V>
    Implements calculation of Euclidean distance between two multi-dimensional points.
    HaversineDistance<V>
    Implements calculation of Haversine distance between two 2-dimensional points.
    JaccardDistance<V>
    Implements calculation of Jaccard distance between two equi-sized sets of tokens (keywords).
    ManhattanDistance<V>
    Implements calculation of Manhattan distance between two multi-dimensional points.
